{"tid":138860,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[diu u ching ar!] SELFLY 自拍無人機兼任手機殼　79 美元親民價眾籌現身","createTime":"2017-03-01T03:03:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T03:37:56.000Z","uid":9348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5f1ff52eea338fe46321394454f4e795e5776e3","tid":138860,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T03:03:16.000Z","msg":"SELFLY 自拍無人機兼任手機殼　79 美元親民價眾籌現身<br />\n<br />\n自拍無人機愈來愈便攜，近日眾籌網站 Kickstarter 出現只有手機般大小的航拍機 SELFLY，折疊後可放進手機殼，一物兩用之餘，性價比可能是更吸引人的地方。<br />\n<br />\n折後體積形同手機<br />\nSELFLY 航拍機方便在於可以與用家的手機共用同一個保護殼，一起放在口袋內。SELFLY 本體只厚 9 毫米，重 70 克；4 個軸臂向內折疊後，便能放進保護殼上的專用凹槽，另一邊則是放置用戶自己的手機，容易收納和隨身攜帶。Apple iPhone、Samsung Galaxy S6 Edge、Google Nexus 6 等受歡迎型號有專用手機殼，同時亦有 4 至 6 吋機適用的通用版本。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d1z0nyenkjpb9t-cloudfront-net.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/d1z0nyenkjpb9t.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/selfly2-800x587.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd1z0nyenkjpb9t-cloudfront-net.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fd1z0nyenkjpb9t.cloudfront.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2Fselfly2-800x587.jpg&h=93c9d937&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSELFLY 機如其名，就是主打自拍的無人機。<br />\n<br />\n內置跟拍功能<br />\n如零度智控 Dobby 一樣，SELFLY 號稱可在掌上升降，內置先進增穩技術、自動飛行系統，除了在 app 用遙桿模式控制，亦可選擇 Fly by Picture，跟蹤拍攝主體。SELFLY 配備 800 萬像素鏡頭，能拍攝 1080p @ 30fps 影片；用上 650 mAh 電池，連續飛行時間只有約 5 分鐘，大概能拍攝 20 張照片，但 SELFLY 創辦人 Hagay Klein 認為已夠自拍一晚。<br />\n<br />\n早前概念非常類似的 AirSelfie 已在 Kickstarter 成功眾籌，兩者皆以體積細小、兼任手機殼、方便自拍為賣點，但功能相比下 SELFLY 無疑比 AirSelfie 優勝。<br />\n<br />\nKickstarter Lin: <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/selfly/selfly-camera-the-smart-flying-phone-case-camera\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fprojects%2Fselfly%2Fselfly-camera-the-smart-flying-phone-case-camera&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=c12eaaae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/selfly/selfly-camera-the-smart-flying-phone-case-camera</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a5dd6408c5b3b3594d886a6e0bde4f764cf4b7","tid":138860,"uid":7923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T03:27:52.000Z","msg":"好有性趣"},{"pid":"e68fa52e91e8703225e205bbfe20ca1eacc090e4","tid":138860,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T03:31:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好有性趣</blockquote><br />\n而家得返99個us大洋既reward<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非你搵到4個frd子一齊買"},{"pid":"8d1e558c66bda4c34ce7618a5aefb398d1e88c9d","tid":138860,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T03:33:01.000Z","msg":"宣傳片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_-_jwOTex-o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_-_jwOTex-o&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=0c188225\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_-_jwOTex-o</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Is3UpsOed0U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIs3UpsOed0U&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=50647266\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Is3UpsOed0U</a><br />\n<br />\ndemo<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ehp1F2ClUec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEhp1F2ClUec&d=JyEZwpqAG2Vgd3IXgRp6kb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=7163e6f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ehp1F2ClUec</a>"},{"pid":"469a1547c9b00b2a9a0418936e76609411f4a61f","tid":138860,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T03:37:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/015/288/398/471be35c407d4ef75f087080cecaa482_original.jpg?w=700&amp;fit=max&amp;v=1485384542&amp;auto=format&amp;q=92&amp;s=dc76e50608767215e7e0b28828a97e46\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fksr-ugc.imgix.net%2Fassets%2F015%2F288%2F398%2F471be35c407d4ef75f087080cecaa482_original.jpg